after them

1. *Vrsta* je određena kvalitetom, ukusom i bojom. (The type is determined by quality, taste and color.)
2. Ovo je sasvim nova *vrsta* proizvoda. (This is a completely new type of product.)
3. Oni su se razdvojili u dve *vrste*. (They split into two types.)
4. Svaka *vrsta* mesa ima drugačiju teksturu. (Each type of meat has a different texture.)
5. *Vrsta* ribe je bila nepoznata. (The type of fish was unknown.)
6. U prirodi postoje razne *vrste* biljaka. (In nature there are various types of plants.)
7. Ovo je jedna od retkih *vrsta* ptica. (This is one of the rare types of birds.)
8. Ova *vrsta* obuće se ne prodaje u našoj trgovini. (This type of shoes is not sold in our store.)